import React from 'react';
import { BrowserRouter as Router, Switch, Route, Link} from 'react-router-dom'
import { Container, Row, Col } from 'react-bootstrap'
import NavHeader from "./NavHeader"
import Body from './Body'

function App() {
  return (
    <Container fluid>
      <Row>
          <Col xl={1}></Col>
                    <Col>
                      <NavHeader />
                    </Col>
          <Col></Col>
      </Row>
      <Row>
          <Col xl={1}></Col>
                  <Col>
                    <Body />
                  </Col>
          <Col></Col>
      </Row>
    </Container>
  );
}

export default App;
